descp2: An optional `string`. Defaults to `""`. string specifying a hint about the algorithm used for decompression.  Defaults to "" which maps to a system-specific default.  Currently valid values are ["INTEGER_FAST", "INTEGER_ACCURATE"].  The hint may be ignored (e.g., the internal jpeg library changes to a version that does not have that specific option.)
